body:
> Does this happen every time for the same .xlsx files? Or does it upload sometimes?

I went back to a log from a couple of months ago, and the same file (redacted to `file.xlsx`, but it matches the file you excerpted above) copied. We didn't have verbose logging enabled at the time.

```
{"level":"debug","msg":"Need to transfer - File not found at Destination","object":"file.xlsx","objectType":"*drive.documentObject","source":"sync/sync.go:1248","time":"2025-03-01T20:35:49.215855-08:00"}
{"level":"debug","msg":"Starting multipart upload","object":"file.xlsx","objectType":"*onedrive.Object","source":"onedrive/onedrive.go:2515","time":"2025-03-01T20:36:20.608689-08:00"}
{"level":"debug","msg":"Uploading segment 0/13707 size 13707","object":"file.xlsx","objectType":"*onedrive.Object","source":"onedrive/onedrive.go:2540","time":"2025-03-01T20:36:21.215131-08:00"}
{"level":"debug","msg":"Size and modification time the same (differ by -972ms, within tolerance 1s)","object":"file.xlsx","objectType":"*object.StaticObjectInfo","source":"operations/operations.go:291","time":"2025-03-01T20:36:22.273455-08:00"}
{"level":"debug","msg":"Updating size of doc after download to 13707","object":"file.xlsx","objectType":"*drive.documentObject","source":"drive/drive.go:4225","time":"2025-03-01T20:36:22.273455-08:00"}
{"level":"info","msg":"Copied (Rcat, new)","object":"file.xlsx","objectType":"*drive.documentObject","size":13707,"source":"operations/copy.go:368","time":"2025-03-01T20:36:22.273455-08:00"}
```

This run was the first one, and there were no errors for any of the files. Could it be a problem when files exist on the target but need to be updated?

> Does it happen with any other sort of files?

I've only seen it for `.xlsx` files. Here are some forum topics that also mention this file type associated with the same error.

- https://forum.rclone.org/t/running-copy-sync-commands-cause-sharepoint-files-to-get-nixed-itemnotfound-the-upload-session-was-not-found/28541
- https://forum.rclone.org/t/sharepoint-upload-xls-files-404-not-found/49136
- https://forum.rclone.org/t/issue-with-uploading-xlsx-and-txt-file-to-sharepoint/46100

> Can you reproduce on any other sharepoints?

I can't test with these files going into another SharePoint site, and I've not seen it in other sites I test with.
